# Cursor AI Rules — Tech Portal
# These rules are also compatible with other AI coding assistants.

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15 (App Router, TypeScript, static export)
- Vanilla CSS with custom properties (NO Tailwind)
- AWS CloudFront + S3 via Terraform
- GitHub Actions CI/CD

## Coding Standards
- TypeScript strict mode, no `any`
- Named exports for components
- Path aliases: `@/*` → `./src/*`
- BEM naming for CSS: `.block__element--modifier`
- CSS tokens via `var(--custom-property)`
- Server Components by default

## File Conventions
- Components: `src/components/PascalCase.tsx`
- Pages: `src/app/**/page.tsx`
- Styles: `src/app/globals.css` (design system)
- Infrastructure: `infra/*.tf`

## Important
- This is a STATIC site (output: 'export') — no API routes
- All images must be unoptimized
- Use `trailingSlash: true` in URLs
